import React, { Component } from 'react';

class WalletForm extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <form>
        <label htmlFor="value">
          Valor:
          <input
            data-testid="value-input"
            name="value"
            type="number"
          />
        </label>
        <label htmlFor="description">
          Descrição:
          <input
            data-testid="description-input"
            name="description"
            type="text"
          />
        </label>
        <label htmlFor="currency">
          Moeda:
          <select
            data-testid="value-input"
            name="currency"
          />
        </label>
      </form>
    );
  }
}

export default WalletForm;
